WEBVTT



00:00:10.912 --> 00:00:11.776
Hello.

00:00:11.584 --> 00:00:20.576
I'm Derek Walker. I'm a Bible teacher and the senior pastor of the Oxford Bible Church. It's my pleasure today to introduce my book to you.

00:00:20.512 --> 00:00:27.136
It's called Getting Healed: A Guide to Receive Your Healing and it's published by Destiny Image Europe.

00:00:27.008 --> 00:00:37.056
And I believe that the revelation that it contains will make all the difference to your ability to receive healing from God as well as to help others

00:00:36.576 --> 00:00:37.952
Get healed.

00:00:38.240 --> 00:00:40.096
And we all need healing.

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:41.344
And health, you say.

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:48.096
Both for our personal happiness and well-being, as well as for us to fulfil the will of God for our life.

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:50.368
Yet, for many people,

00:00:50.592 --> 00:00:55.456
Healing is a mysterious subject. They see it as a hit or miss affair.

00:00:55.264 --> 00:00:58.944
And so they find it hard to trust God for their healing.

00:00:58.784 --> 00:01:01.344
And this book is written for you.

00:01:01.248 --> 00:01:06.784
Because it will clear away all the cobwebs of doubt and confusion,

00:01:06.592 --> 00:01:09.760
And you might have concerning the subject of healing.

00:01:10.112 --> 00:01:15.904
So that you will find yourself able to walk by faith in the healing power of God.

00:01:15.712 --> 00:01:18.912
And so enjoy his life, his health, his strength.

00:01:19.264 --> 00:01:21.952
You know, God passionately loves you.

00:01:21.792 --> 00:01:23.872
And he desires to heal you.

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:27.552
In Exodus 15 he declares, "I am the Lord your healer."

00:01:27.488 --> 00:01:30.208
I am the Lord who heals you.

00:01:30.656 --> 00:01:33.824
The Bible talks about a wonderful river.

00:01:33.728 --> 00:01:39.072
of healing power, the river of life that contains God's healing power.

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:41.664
And it promises that whosoever

00:01:41.440 --> 00:01:45.664
can freely drink of it and so receive God's life and health.

00:01:46.144 --> 00:01:52.224
But to do this, we need the confidence that comes from knowing God's Word.

00:01:52.672 --> 00:02:01.472
From my research in the subject, I've discovered that there are four keys, four areas of knowledge that need to be established in our hearts.

00:02:01.184 --> 00:02:05.248
In order for us to be able to confidently receive our healing,

00:02:05.152 --> 00:02:08.640
And in this book, I give you those keys.

00:02:08.544 --> 00:02:10.592
And once you have them,

00:02:10.496 --> 00:02:15.488
you will find that God's reservoirs of healing will be opened up to you.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:20.864
I share not just about how to get healed, but also how to stay healed.

00:02:20.960 --> 00:02:31.008
and I give a number of testimonies to show how God's healing power actually works including the story of my wife Hilary who was dramatically healed of her

00:02:30.528 --> 00:02:32.512
Of rheumatoid arthritis.

00:02:32.608 --> 00:02:40.256
Getting healed will give you the foundation you need to consistently receive healing and health every day of your life.

00:02:39.968 --> 00:02:41.600
It will lead you.

00:02:41.376 --> 00:02:43.296
Into the truths

00:02:43.008 --> 00:02:53.056
that will set you free from sickness and disease. It will lead you into the presence of the Lord who heals you. And that's why I recommend that you honor your company.

00:02:52.576 --> 00:02:53.376
I'm copying it all

00:02:54.016 --> 00:02:56.960
May God's blessing of healing and health be with you.

